			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Speak to Hastar Biggs - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group2_Prisoner2 ec0de12d-4a2f-4683-bb11-91473ec3577c - (37; 39; 70)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Quick setup:&#xD;&#xA;- Load CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)&#xD;&#xA;- Set Quest Flags and Options -&gt; Act3 (LOW) -&gt; Iron Throne -&gt; Change State -&gt; Back At Docks -&gt; MajoritySaved&#xD;&#xA;- Then talk to the NPC" />
